title: Number of homicide offences in England and Wales 2002 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of homicides offences. In total the number of data points it has is 17.
In general Number of homicides offences has fallen over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2015/16 and 2016/17.
Maximum Number of homicides offences, about 1047.0 was reported at Year 2002/03
Minimum Number of homicides offences about 533.0 was reached at Year 2013/14
